===Etymology===
From {{etyl|si}} {{term|sc=Sinh|ශ්‍රී ලංකාව|tr=śrī laṃkā|lang=si}}, from {{etyl|sa}} {{term|sc=Deva|श्री||holy|tr=śrī|lang=sa}} and {{term|sc=Deva|लंका||island|tr=lankā|lang=sa}}.

===Pronunciation===
